		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Seems the PM games default to MONO sound in the settings. This has the GBSs being ripped to the same settings.
<br />
<br />It's not a terribly hard fix to implement, as long as you know the stereo address in RAM, and can work with the files.
<br />
<br />I've done PM Yellow and Crystal, check my site. If you find any other MONO sound games with a stereo option, I can probably fix them with little effort.

		

		</td>
